Polaroid to use Creo Products machines . Polaroid Corp said Wednesday its graphics imaging division has entered into an agreement to use Creo Products Inc ' s computer - to - plate machines for use in printing Polaroid ' s dry , digital film . The agreement allows Polaroid ' s Dry Tech Imagesetting film to be printed on Creo ' s line of Trendsetters , the company said . Terms were not disclosed . Creo Products Inc is based in Burnaby , British Columbia . 
